entry.def: Decals are pieces of paper with a design on one side. The design can be transferred onto a surface by heating it, soaking it in water, or pressing it hard.

means.word_mean: 1. a design fixed to some surface or a paper bearing the design to be transferred to the surface
2. the art of transfering designs from specially prepared paper to a wood or glass or metal surface
